 3800, 0), (68674, 'Always work on extending your territory and capacity', 3800, 0), (68675, 'Our main mandate in our place of work is to make sure that the people open up their hearts to others', 3800, 0), (68676, 'Use your influence to make impact and help others grow', 3800, 0), (68677, 'Use your work as a platform to bring the principles of God to the people', 3800, 0), (68678, 'Be a source of influence to others', 3800, 0), (68679, 'Be a history maker', 3800, 0), (68680, 'Impact people’s lives positively', 3800, 0), (68681, 'Let your ways and actions be in honor of Christ', 3800, 0), (68682, 'You can’t change the world if you don’t know the principles of God', 3800, 0), (68683, 'We shouldn’t use God for our purpose alone but also be instruments of the extension of His Kingdom', 3800, 0), (68684, 'Expand your vision and widen your reasoning', 3800, 0), (68685, 'Employment is world slavery', 3800, 0), (68686, 'You need to answer questions on where, when and what to do', 3800, 0), (68687, 'Go to the root of the problems of people and discover ways to save them', 3800, 0), (68688, 'Make your life a meaningful one', 3800, 0), (68689, 'Product must be intentional', 3800, 0), (68690, 'Joblessness releases you from the world system', 3800, 0), (68691, 'You can be the solution to the problems of the people', 3800, 0), (68692, 'Employment should not be your permanent assignment', 3800, 0), (68693, 'Joblessness gives you life ownership', 3800, 0), (68694, 'Life becomes a blessing when you discover your calling', 3800, 0), (68695, 'Don’t try to use God to achieve your purpose. Rather, aim to achieve His', 3800, 0), (68696, 'We were created to use our lives as an instrument and everything we have to extend God’s Kingdom', 3800, 0), (68697, 'God does not just save you for your personal interest but for you to become a channel for the salvation of others', 3800, 0), (68698, 'Once you become delivered, you have to find your calling and how to discover God’s purpose for your li